The paper discusses the problem of novelty detection, which is a core component of several research areas such as fraud detection, intrusion detection, medical diagnosis, data cleaning, and fault prevention. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
